# Supabase Realtime — powers the online arena (play a friend, standard + Duck Chess).
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the two values from your Supabase project
# (Settings → API). Both are public-by-design: the anon key ships in the client bundle and
# the game channel is unauthenticated (anyone with the project URL + a game id can join), which
# is fine for a private invite link shared between two friends. Leave unset to disable online
# play locally — the app still runs (lessons, glossary, arena vs. engine, local hot-seat).
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
